{"tid":547453,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門狗真係零舍on9過人","createTime":"2018-02-01T12:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T06:35:45.000Z","uid":12034,"like":73,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb0160d4636e863409aeff8f193ed29a15b8fe7","tid":547453,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.mastvnet.com/news/macau/culture/2018-01-29/45677.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mastvnet.com%2Fnews%2Fmacau%2Fculture%2F2018-01-29%2F45677.html&d=Nq4rm%2BKG4QyDEazL37dGdywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=fb8120c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mastvnet.com/news/macau/culture/2018-01-29/45677.html</a><br />\n<br />\n這次大力神盃首度訪澳，由於隻開放一天參觀，吸引大批市民一早排隊等候入場。官方原定在中午12點30分開放入場，但中間發生一段小插曲，主辦方稱由於系統事故，開放時間要延至下午3時，原本滿心歡喜朝聖，當得悉有機會失望而回，排頭位的市民都忍不住流下男兒淚。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母喊到死老豆咁 笑撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b980c33c106382a26afe134192fbc50b324b7062","tid":547453,"uid":4492,"like":71,"dislike":3,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"澳門人既作用<br />\n男-荷官，馬伕<br />\n女-荷官，雞"},{"pid":"24baf6b88efb6fc90d84aa582936e1b32b12e7cd","tid":547453,"uid":32938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2fba6a231bd0c54151a0b478afdc57465d1d69","tid":547453,"uid":1734,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"b980c33c106382a26afe134192fbc50b324b7062","tid":547453,"uid":4492,"like":71,"dislike":3,"score":68,"citedBy